summary: THE VEHICLES HEADLIGHTS AND DAYTIME RUNNING LIGHTS FAILED 3 DAY PRIOR TO RECEIVING THE RECALL NOTICE.  ONCE THE RECALL WAS PERFORMED THE DAYTIME RUNNING LIGHTS STILL DID NOT WORK AND THE AIR BAG LIGHT WAS ILLUMINATING.  THEN WHEN THE CONSUMER ATTEMPTED TO USE THE HIGH BEAMS ALL THE EXTERIOR AND INTERIOR LIGHT WENT OUT (1996 VOLKSWAGEN PASSAT).  NLM
